org.xbib.pipeline

Interface PipelineExecutor<T,R extends PipelineRequest,P extends Pipeline<T,R>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the result type
    R - the request type
    P - the pipeline type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetricQueuePipelineExecutor, MetricSimplePipelineExecutor, QueuePipelineExecutor, SimplePipelineExecutor

    public interface PipelineExecutor<T,R extends PipelineRequest,P extends Pipeline<T,R>>
    The Pipeline Executor can execute provided pipelines. If the concurrency level is set to higher than one, more than one pipeline is executed in parallel.
